desmoj.core.report

Class DebugNote

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.core.report.Message
      • desmoj.core.report.DebugNote

  • public class DebugNote
extends Message
    Represents a DebugNote produced by a simulation run whenever the modeller enables the debug mode for a specific ModelComponent. Provides the basic information needed to debug a model's changes of state:
    • The Model this DebugNote originates from
    • The point in simulation time that this DebugNote was issued
    • The name of the ModelComponent that produced the DebugNote
    • The textual debug information produced by that ModelComponent
